{"id":88,"parent_id":52,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":88,"title":"Exodus 36","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ex.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 36"],[".studySummary",["i","Wise-hearted men are chosen to work on the tabernacle—Moses restrains the people from donating any more material."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.1","order":"02.03.036.8544"},["b","1"],"Then wrought",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Bezaleel"],"and Aholiab, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"every wise hearted man"],", in whom the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"put",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"wisdom"],"and understanding to know how to work all manner of work",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"for the service of"],"the sanctuary, according to all that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had commanded."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.2","order":"02.03.036.8545"},["b","2"],"And Moses called Bezaleel and Aholiab, and every wise hearted man, in whose",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"heart"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had put wisdom,",["i","even"],"every one whose heart stirred him up to come unto the work to do it:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.3","order":"02.03.036.8546"},["b","3"],"And they received of Moses all the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"offering"],", which the children of Israel had brought for the work of the service of the sanctuary, to make it",["i","withal."],"And they brought yet unto him",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"free"],"offerings every morning."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.4","order":"02.03.036.8547"},["b","4"],"And all the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"wise"],"men, that wrought all the work of the sanctuary, came every man from his work which they made;"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.5","order":"02.03.036.8548"},["b","5"],"¶And they spake unto Moses, saying, The people",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"bring"],"much more than enough for the service of the work, which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"commanded to make."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.6","order":"02.03.036.8549"},["b","6"],"And Moses gave commandment, and they caused it to be proclaimed throughout the camp, saying, Let neither man nor woman make any more work for the offering of the sanctuary. So the people were restrained from bringing."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.7","order":"02.03.036.8550"},["b","7"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"stuff"],"they had was sufficient for all the work to make it, and too much."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.8","order":"02.03.036.8551"},["b","8"],"¶And every wise hearted man among them that wrought the work of the tabernacle",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"made"],"ten",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"curtains"],["i","of"],"fine twined linen, and blue, and purple, and scarlet:",["i","with"],"cherubims of cunning work made he them."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.9","order":"02.03.036.8552"},["b","9"],"The length of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"one"],"curtain",["i","was"],"twenty and eight cubits, and the breadth of one curtain four cubits: the curtains",["i","were"],"all of one size."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.10","order":"02.03.036.8553"},["b","10"],"And he coupled the five curtains one unto another: and",["i","the other"],"five curtains he coupled one unto another."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.11","order":"02.03.036.8554"},["b","11"],"And he made loops of blue on the edge of one curtain",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"from"],"the selvedge in the coupling: likewise he made in the uttermost side of",["i","another"],"curtain, in the coupling of the second."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.12","order":"02.03.036.8555"},["b","12"],"Fifty loops made he in one curtain, and fifty loops made he in the edge of the curtain which",["i","was"],"in the coupling of the second: the loops held one",["i","curtain"],"to another."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.13","order":"02.03.036.8556"},["b","13"],"And he made fifty",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"taches"],"of gold, and coupled the curtains one unto another with the taches: so it became one tabernacle."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.14","order":"02.03.036.8557"},["b","14"],"¶And he made curtains",["i","of"],"goats’",["i","hair"],"for the tent over the tabernacle: eleven curtains he made them."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.15","order":"02.03.036.8558"},["b","15"],"The length of one curtain",["i","was"],"thirty cubits, and four cubits",["i","was"],"the breadth of one curtain: the eleven curtains",["i","were"],"of one size."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.16","order":"02.03.036.8559"},["b","16"],"And he coupled five curtains by themselves, and six curtains by themselves."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.17","order":"02.03.036.8560"},["b","17"],"And he made fifty loops upon the uttermost edge of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"the"],"curtain in the coupling, and fifty loops made he upon the edge of the curtain which coupleth the second."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.18","order":"02.03.036.8561"},["b","18"],"And he made fifty taches",["i","of"],"brass to couple the tent together, that it might be one."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.19","order":"02.03.036.8562"},["b","19"],"And he made a covering for the tent",["i","of"],"rams’ skins dyed red, and a covering",["i","of"],"badgers’ skins above",["i","that."]],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.20","order":"02.03.036.8563"},["b","20"],"¶And he made",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"boards"],"for the tabernacle",["i","of"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"shittim"],"wood, standing up."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.21","order":"02.03.036.8564"},["b","21"],"The length of a board",["i","was"],"ten cubits, and the breadth of a board one cubit and a half."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.22","order":"02.03.036.8565"},["b","22"],"One board had two tenons,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"equally"],"distant one from another: thus did he make for all the boards of the tabernacle."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.23","order":"02.03.036.8566"},["b","23"],"And he made boards for the tabernacle; twenty boards for the south side southward:"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.24","order":"02.03.036.8567"},["b","24"],"And forty",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"sockets"],"of silver he made under the twenty boards; two sockets under one board for his two tenons, and two sockets under another board for his two tenons."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.25","order":"02.03.036.8568"},["b","25"],"And for the other side of the tabernacle,",["i","which is"],"toward the north corner, he made twenty boards,"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.26","order":"02.03.036.8569"},["b","26"],"And their forty sockets of silver; two sockets under one board, and two sockets under another board."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.27","order":"02.03.036.8570"},["b","27"],"And for the sides of the tabernacle westward he made six boards."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.28","order":"02.03.036.8571"},["b","28"],"And two boards made he for the corners of the tabernacle in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"two sides"],"."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.29","order":"02.03.036.8572"},["b","29"],"And they were coupled beneath, and coupled together at the head thereof, to one ring: thus he did to both of them in both the corners."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.30","order":"02.03.036.8573"},["b","30"],"And there were eight boards; and their sockets",["i","were"],"sixteen sockets of silver, under every board two sockets."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.31","order":"02.03.036.8574"},["b","31"],"¶And he made bars of shittim wood; five for the boards of the one side of the tabernacle,"],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.32","order":"02.03.036.8575"},["b","32"],"And five bars for the boards of the other side of the tabernacle, and five bars for the boards of the tabernacle for the sides westward."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.33","order":"02.03.036.8576"},["b","33"],"And he made the middle bar to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"shoot"],"through the boards from the one end to the other."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.34","order":"02.03.036.8577"},["b","34"],"And he overlaid the boards with gold, and made their rings",["i","of"],"gold",["i","to be"],"places for the bars, and overlaid the bars with gold."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.35","order":"02.03.036.8578"},["b","35"],"¶And he made a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_35a"},"veil"],["i","of"],"blue, and purple, and scarlet, and fine twined linen:",["i","with"],"cherubims made he it of cunning work."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.36","order":"02.03.036.8579"},["b","36"],"And he made thereunto four pillars",["i","of"],"shittim",["i","wood,"],"and overlaid them with gold: their hooks",["i","were of"],"gold; and he cast for them four sockets of silver."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.37","order":"02.03.036.8580"},["b","37"],"¶And he made",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_37a"},"an hanging"],"for the tabernacle door",["i","of"],"blue, and purple, and scarlet, and fine twined linen, of needlework;"],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.38","order":"02.03.036.8581"},["b","38"],"And the five pillars of it with their hooks: and he overlaid their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_38a"},"chapiters"],"and their fillets with gold: but their five sockets",["i","were of"],"brass."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.1a","order":"02.03.036.8582"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/31.2.1-6"},"Ex. 31:2 (1–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.1b","order":"02.03.036.8584"},["b","1b"],["span.small","OR"],"all the able men (see also",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.4"},"v. 4"],")."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.1c","order":"02.03.036.8586"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/35.35"},"Ex. 35:35"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/7.14"},"1 Kgs. 7:14"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-gifts-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Gifts of"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.1d","order":"02.03.036.8588"},["b","1d"],["span.small","IE"],"in the construction of (see also",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.2,8"},"vv. 2, 8"],")."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.2a","order":"02.03.036.8590"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/35.21"},"Ex. 35:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.3a","order":"02.03.036.8592"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/35.24.21-29"},"Ex. 35:24 (21–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.3b","order":"02.03.036.8594"},["b","3b"],["span.small","OR"],"freewill."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.4a","order":"02.03.036.8596"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wisdom"},"TG Wisdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.5a","order":"02.03.036.8598"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/generosity"},"TG Generosity"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.7a","order":"02.03.036.8600"},["b","7a"],["span.small","OR"],"materials."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.8a","order":"02.03.036.8602"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/skill"},"TG Skill"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.8b","order":"02.03.036.8604"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/26.1.1-14"},"Ex. 26:1 (1–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.9a","order":"02.03.036.8606"},["b","9a"],["span.small","OR"],"each."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.11a","order":"02.03.036.8608"},["b","11a"],["span.small","HEB"],"on the outside of the first set."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.13a","order":"02.03.036.8610"},["b","13a"],["span.small","OR"],"clasps."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.17a","order":"02.03.036.8612"},["b","17a"],["span.small","OR"],"the other connecting curtain."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.20a","order":"02.03.036.8614"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/26.15.15-29"},"Ex. 26:15 (15–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.20b","order":"02.03.036.8616"},["b","20b"],["span.small","HEB"],"acacia."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.22a","order":"02.03.036.8618"},["b","22a"],["span.small","HEB"],"which made them fit one to another."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.24a","order":"02.03.036.8620"},["b","24a"],["span.small","OR"],"bases (also",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.26,30,36,38"},"vv. 26, 30, 36, 38"],")."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.28a","order":"02.03.036.8622"},["b","28a"],["span.small","IE"],"those adjoining the west side."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.33a","order":"02.03.036.8624"},["b","33a"],["span.small","OR"],"pass."],["div",{"id":"35a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.35a","order":"02.03.036.8626"},["b","35a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/veil"},"TG Veil"],"."],["div",{"id":"37a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.37a","order":"02.03.036.8628"},["b","37a"],["span.small","OR"],"a screen or curtain."],["div",{"id":"38a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ex/36.38a","order":"02.03.036.8630"},["b","38a"],["span.small","OR"],"capitals or tops of the pillars."]]}
